ARTICLE.TITLE: UN soundly defeats US demand to extend arms embargo on Iran
ARTICLE.TEXT:
Greenville, NC (27833)

Today

Thunderstorms likely. High 89F. Winds SE at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 80%..

Tonight

Thunderstorms likely this evening. Then a chance of scattered thunderstorms overnight. Low 72F. Winds light and variable. Chance of rain 80%. Locally heavy rainfall possible.

METADATA.description: UNITED NATIONS (AP) — The U.N. Security Council on Friday resoundingly defeated a U.S. resolution to indefinitely extend the U.N. arms embargo on Iran, with the Trump administration getting support
METADATA.author: EDITH M. LEDERER Associated Press
